  "text": "Cloud computing has brought about the concept of computing as a utility, making software, platform and infrastructure to be sold as services. Companies and developers that have business on the Internet do not need to worry about computational infrastructure to bring their projects into operation. The infrastructure can be leased in a cloud provider, which handle different demands of workloads and prevent resources from remaining idle or overloaded [CITATION_1] .",
